    "body": "I think this has nothing to do with the actual truffle framework since the erroneous line is in your test file. You have used ES6 module loading syntax which is not supported in v8.4.0 of nodejs (your version) nor in v9.2.0 (current latest).\r\n\r\nThe only way to make ES6 modules work is by using transpiler/compiler like `babel`.",
