    "body": "I think registering load hooks within the module system won't work around this issue anymore. All scripts now seem to be loaded through [truffle-require](https://github.com/trufflesuite/truffle/blob/develop/packages/truffle-require/require.js), and this imports `original-require` which gets a handle on `require` prior to any code in `truffle.js` being executed.\r\n\r\nEnd result is any changes you make to the module loading system will no longer be reflected by scripts that truffle loads in.",
